    "The variable Base I is the set of individuals that compose the collectivity.",
    "Other denominations for the Base would be the Board, the Constituency, the Collectivity, the Community.",
    "The institution of the polity determines who counts as member of the collectivity, and those who count form the Base.",
    "An element of the Base will be called an agent.",
    "Other denominations would be: member, citizen, party."
  ],
